data.description: Welcome Home! This Beautiful, Updated 4 Bed, 2.5 Bath Home in Chicago's South Suburb of Crete is waiting for you! This Home has Hardwood Floors on the first floor. The windows let in lots of natural light, and the kitchen is spacious with a big picture window that looks out into the large yard. Entertain guests on the Patio, or indoor Bar! There is a large farmhouse door that can separate the space for quiet and privacy. The Second Floor features a huge Master Bedroom with Double Closets, a Full Bath, a second bedroom with lots of storage, plus a possible 5th bedroom! Craftsmanship and Care shows throughout this home. Come see it today! (1 Year Home Warranty Included!)
